rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但鹽就到宜家都未掌握到<br />\n成日都覺得自己已經起勢咁落到食左個腎會唔會有事<br />\n但都係得少少味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我每次整出黎啲野食都係好淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a3ead1150e00c8307058acffd4f7dbf6964d40","tid":1899704,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T21:42:35.000Z","msg":"整意粉 最簡單"},{"pid":"05534973da6d7001988343494bf331aabcc1e1ab","tid":1899704,"uid":280153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebc92adb05aa045a5a2b8e0f36587a104672c23e","tid":1899704,"uid":49955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T19:00:03.000Z","msg":"學左點樣唔痴鑊先<br />\n鑊燒到一個地步放水珠落去唔會滾，會變成水珠look黎look去就肯定夠熱<br />\n油就要燒到起油紋，甚至有油煙（過煙點會致癌，起煙就快啲落料）<br />\n鑊夠熱油夠熱就唔痴<br />\n<br />\n煎野炒野都係熱左鑊先落油，炒滑蛋唔可以太熱果啲就熱鑊凍油<br />\n<br />\n煮煮下就識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T21:57:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再講多啲，想知刀工點搞..."},{"pid":"d28b785dd7f50af2816d112f36893bd05e254941","tid":1899704,"uid":280153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T21:59:20.000Z","msg":"我睇YouTube 好似好易，但次次都失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解有啲人煮食咁叻咁勁"},{"pid":"46049d4488e26453b610302dd79a4c0c8732029a","tid":1899704,"uid":89869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dbdc5d3e55d24642fff16fc465b25e53c33a7cbd","tid":1899704,"uid":185304,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"