:137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:26:29.000Z","msg":"我睇 youtube 20無限<br />\n貪佢夠hea 似家常便飯 容易煮"},{"pid":"eb81d1b39ab4deb607d0f411c045d3a36c869e1b","tid":1899704,"uid":93069,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dbdc5d3e55d24642fff16fc465b25e53c33a7cbd","tid":1899704,"uid":185304,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T19:04:04.000Z","msg":"馬田叔叔幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:31:40.000Z","msg":"errr... martin theory 多 實戰唔係好得咖喎<br />\n記得有一集佢d嘉賓話佢煮出黎既唔太得 唔好食<br />\n我自己都有跟過佢1 2個recipe 成品都麻麻<br />\n建議睇bob叔 中西菜都有 西會多d<br />\n試過跟佢做5 6個菜 全部都好好食"},{"pid":"44e6c02bab562bfbafaf80923cca70d0c479aad6","tid":1899704,"uid":231522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:33:14.000Z","msg":"YouTube大把<br />\n刀功切多D就得 自己食，冇必要好似大師傅咁"},{"pid":"3e39d7a4d9f13d05c2f55e104f988d4fe8d6fb86","tid":1899704,"uid":23895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d995b43651813755b7f31057c6588ed73dd65419","tid":1899704,"uid":70338,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"dbdc5d3e55d24642fff16fc465b25e53c33a7cbd","tid":1899704,"uid":185304,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T19:04:04.000Z","msg":"馬田叔叔幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T21:35:47.000Z","msg":"真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢幾個月悶到日日都係屋企整野食<br />\n本來跌埋心水以後做無飯主婦<br />\n但跟住馬田煮左幾樣都ok<br />\n不過中菜就要睇呀媽級youtuber會好啲<br />\n<br />\n我覺得煮野食比先想像中易<br />\n煩係煩在新手煮完一餐 好似要將成個廚房嘅碗碟都洗過曬咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有最難係鹽同油嘅份量<br />\n第一二次煮嘅時候 覺得自己已經落左勁多油 點知都係未夠多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但鹽就到宜家都未掌握到<br />\n成日都覺得自己已經起勢咁落到食左個腎會唔會有事<br />\n但都係得少少味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我每次整出黎啲野食都係好淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:35:01.000Z","msg":"一路煮一路試味，唔試點知夠唔夠味"},{"pid":"c68e47df3dc9f32b73e447d87a464dc282b21d68","tid":1899704,"uid":269009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:36:01.000Z","msg":"Youtube學"},{"pid":"03c36d2e202f38e93269b1f1846d0792efd1c9d8","tid":1899704,"uid":230177,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:46:34.000Z","msg":"我自己一開始就睇下bob叔 唔熟唔食 ，頭幾次都煮得好難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大約煮左半年先開始識下點煮 。<br />\n之後前排比公司炒左 去左朋友間餐廳做下廚房 順便學下點煮嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做左一兩個月後 依家煮嘢最少唔難食 食得入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女朋友都話我依家煮得唔錯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12418ac8bb047d5765053719c8808331087171e3","tid":1899704,"uid":70338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e39d7a4d9f13d05c2f55e104f988d4fe8d6fb86","tid":1899704,"uid":23895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d995b43651813755b7f31057c6588ed73dd65419","tid":1899704,"uid":70338,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"dbdc5d3e55d24642fff16fc465b25e53c33a7cbd","tid":1899704,"uid":185304,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T19:04:04.000Z","msg":"馬田叔叔幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.