 /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bdeb71f2eeeccd45d75f58b5ecf626263cd7d38","tid":1899704,"uid":130228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T08:59:19.000Z","msg":"西餐入門睇邊個channel好??"},{"pid":"a9dc3e1ca59dcb810b6966847070b4f2e4aafd66","tid":1899704,"uid":89869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44e6c02bab562bfbafaf80923cca70d0c479aad6","tid":1899704,"uid":231522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:33:14.000Z","msg":"YouTube大把<br />\n刀功切多D就得 自己食，冇必要好似大師傅咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T09:48:54.000Z","msg":"麵tv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485bcb7eb7e5ad6d69249501ed69a82dd0469328","tid":1899704,"uid":23895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12418ac8bb047d5765053719c8808331087171e3","tid":1899704,"uid":70338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e39d7a4d9f13d05c2f55e104f988d4fe8d6fb86","tid":1899704,"uid":23895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d995b43651813755b7f31057c6588ed73dd65419","tid":1899704,"uid":70338,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T21:35:47.000Z","msg":"真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢幾個月悶到日日都係屋企整野食<br />\n本來跌埋心水以後做無飯主婦<br />\n但跟住馬田煮左幾樣都ok<br />\n不過中菜就要睇呀媽級youtuber會好啲<br />\n<br />\n我覺得煮野食比先想像中易<br />\n煩係煩在新手煮完一餐 好似要將成個廚房嘅碗碟都洗過曬咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有最難係鹽同油嘅份量<br />\n第一二次煮嘅時候 覺得自己已經落左勁多油 點知都係未夠多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但鹽就到宜家都未掌握到<br />\n成日都覺得自己已經起勢咁落到食左個腎會唔會有事<br />\n但都係得少少味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" 